  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/a66b9d4ec79cca23d45b14b14235717b.webp?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br><br><strong>Jitsu Squad</strong> is a 4 player co-op beat ‘em up with fast-paced cartoony action and wacky chaotic battles! It has the accessibility and classic brawler mechanics of games like <strong>Streets of Rage</strong> and <strong>Final Fight</strong> but with the speed and intensity of fighting games games such as<strong> Marvel vs. Capcom II, Dragonball FighterZ & Super Smash Bros.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/98155c0a52e31e258274cfd3817d11a9.webp?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br><br>This mode makes it possible to switch between playable characters. You can control the entire Jitsu Squad on a single quest or play with a friend and choose two characters each! The combo possibilities are insane and so satisfying!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/ec5888a2a2b9f59cfe26d9cbf9738ca4.poster.avif?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/ec5888a2a2b9f59cfe26d9cbf9738ca4.webm?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/ec5888a2a2b9f59cfe26d9cbf9738ca4.mp4?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/82311daacc6ab507954ba88472e74079.webp?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br><br>Collect enough soul orbs and put on your <strong>ULTIMATE ARMOR!</strong> You become invincible and all your attacks and special moves become stronger than ever for a short period of time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/694770c09935ed9658fe4ff11f230c1b.poster.avif?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/694770c09935ed9658fe4ff11f230c1b.webm?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/694770c09935ed9658fe4ff11f230c1b.mp4?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/d438c05d09d168464f59d5997f5d7b75.webp?t=1670606330\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br><br>\t•\tEpic Super Specials!<br>\t•\t500+ chain-combos!<br>\t•\tPowerful in-game character transformations!<br>\t•\tAwesome crossover assist characters!<br>\t•\tRun or Dash! No walking allowed in Jitsu Squad<br>\t•\tA wide variety of unique enemies and stages!<br>\t•\tUp to 4-player co-op fun!<br>\t•\tUnique secondary weapons for each playable character!<br>\t•\tUpgrade system to level up your character!<br>\t•\tInfinite juggles<br>\t•\tParrying/Counters<br>\t•\tTAG TEAM MODE!<br>\t•\tFURY MODE!<br>\t•\tAnd more to come!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/cfc376004f1856e05228a8c9f053be98.poster.avif?t=1670606330\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/cfc376004f1856e05228a8c9f053be98.webm?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522080/extras/cfc376004f1856e05228a8c9f053be98.mp4?t=1670606330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
